  "body": "when I run the command line in the terminal\r\n```\r\nyarn hardhat test\r\n```\r\nIt lasts  about 6 mintes, \r\nbut it's very quickly when  I type\r\n```\r\nyarn hardhat coverage\r\n```\r\n\r\nI retype  the command-line \r\n\r\n```\r\n    yarn hardhat test  --verbose --show-stack-traces\r\n```\r\nAnd the line will pause on the line for 5 minutes.\r\n```\r\n  hardhat:core:analytics Hit for \"/task/builtin\" sent successfully +604ms\r\n```\r\nand the following line is :\r\n```\r\nhardhat:core:hre Running test:run-mocha-tests's super +3m\r\n```\r\n\r\nMy Package.json file is \r\n```\r\n    \"@chainlink/contracts\": \"^0.5.1\",\r\n    \"@nomicfoundation/hardhat-network-helpers\": \"^1.0.6\",\r\n    \"@nomiclabs/hardhat-ethers\": \"npm:hardhat-deploy-ethers\",\r\n    \"@nomiclabs/hardhat-etherscan\": \"^3.1.2\",\r\n    \"@nomiclabs/hardhat-waffle\": \"^2.0.3\",\r\n    \"chai\": \"^4.3.6\",\r\n    \"ethereum-waffle\": \"^3.2.0\",\r\n    \"ethers\": \"^5.7.2\",\r\n    \"hardhat\": \"^2.12.2\",\r\n    \"hardhat-deploy\": \"^0.11.19\",\r\n    \"hardhat-gas-reporter\": \"^1.0.9\",\r\n    \"solhint\": \"^3.3.7\",\r\n    \"solidity-coverage\": \"^0.8.2\"\r\n```\r\n\r\nMy computer Configuration\r\nMacBook Pro  i5 , 16G DDR\r\nMacOS catalina  10.15.7\r\nNode version : v16.13.1\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
